OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FThe PSNI Chief Constable has vowed to
OL,8,F"relentlessly pursue" officers abusing
OL,9,Ftheir position for sexual purposes
OL,10,Fafter a report found evidence of
OL,11,Fpredatory behaviour in the police.
OL,13,FJon Boutcher told the policing board
OL,14,Fthat such incidents make him and the
OL,15,Fsenior team "so angry" and serve to
OL,16,F"undermine everything we're trying to
OL,17,Fachieve".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]wD@MOUwD@VO]xD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FA report published this week analysed
OL,8,Fallegations involving officers (all
OL,9,Fmale and aged between 30 and 50)
OL,10,Fbetween 2018 and 2024.
OL,12,FIt found predatory behaviour features
OL,13,Fin 30% of the most serious cases
OL,14,Finvestigated by the Police Ombudsman
OL,15,Ffor Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FThe report also highlighted the
OL,8,Fvulnerabilities of the 36 victims (all
OL,9,Ffemale) identified in the cases, from
OL,10,Fbeing a victim of crime, to mental
OL,11,Fhealth issues, domestic abuse,
OL,12,Fsuicidal ideation or addiction.
OL,14,FThere was evidence of targeted
OL,15,Fexploitation of women, with police
OL,16,Fofficers in those cases often making
OL,17,Finappropriate use of police systems to
OL,18,Fidentify women for sexual exploitation
OL,19,For acquire further information in
OL,20,Frelation to potential victims.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FIn his opening remarks to the board on
OL,8,FThursday, Mr Boutcher said "any abuse
OL,9,Fof position for sexual purposes is not
OL,10,Fsimply wholly unacceptable, it's
OL,11,Fabhorrent".
OL,13,FHe said: "It represents the most
OL,14,Fegregious breach of trust and a
OL,15,Fviolation of the standards we expect
OL,16,Fof police officers and staff."
OL,18,FHe added: "I want to reassure this
OL,19,Fboard and everyone watching that we
OL,20,Fwill relentlessly pursue and deal with
OL,21,Fthese people.
OL,26,@pD@\OUsD@JO]uD@JOUxD@^O]zD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"Our collective commitment as a senior
OL,8,Fteam and as an organisation is for
OL,9,Fzero tolerance for this type of
OL,10,Factivity.
OL,12,F"While the ombudsman's report
OL,13,Fidentifies serious individual
OL,14,Fmisconduct, importantly, very
OL,15,Fimportantly, it very much recognises
OL,16,Fthe positive strategic direction we
OL,17,Fhave taken and the significant work
OL,18,Fdone to strengthen professional
OL,19,Fstandards, enhance vetting and
OL,20,Fmisconduct reporting processes and for
OL,21,Flearning from past failures."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FThe Chief Constable said the
OL,8,Forganisation "will do everything
OL,9,Fnecessary to deal with such issues"
OL,10,Fbut that "the numbers of these
OL,11,Fofficers are numerically incredibly
OL,12,Fsmall".
OL,14,F"Albeit any such officer, even one, is
OL,15,Funacceptable," he said.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@cO]rD@JOUtD@FO]vD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"The vast majority of our people are
OL,8,Famazing and are more disgusted at this
OL,9,Fbehaviour than anyone, because it
OL,10,Fundermines who we are and what we're
OL,11,Fhere to do ` to protect society and
OL,12,Flook after vulnerable people, not
OL,13,Fexploit them."
OL,15,FMr Boutcher added: "There is no place
OL,16,Ffor these people in the PSNI, we will
OL,17,Ffind them and we will sack them."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@NO]wD@TOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FPolitical representatives on the
OL,8,Fboard, Alliance MLA Nuala McAllister
OL,9,Fand Sinn Fein MLA Linda Dillon, both
OL,10,Fraised concerns on the findings of the
OL,11,Fombudsman's report.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FMr Boutcher replied: "When I arrived
OL,8,Fhere I was concerned about the levels
OL,9,Fof misogyny in society here, and I
OL,10,Fdon't know if that's simply because
OL,11,Fit's more prevalent here, or simply
OL,12,Fbecause I've not noticed that
OL,13,Fprevalence increase generally in
OL,14,Fsociety, because of the online harms
OL,15,Fthat we see and the way mainly young
OL,16,Fmen are being shown things that nobody
OL,17,Fshould look at through the internet,
OL,18,Fand being developed into people who
OL,19,Fbecome bad adults, as opposed to good,
OL,20,Fpositive members of the community."
OL,26,@oD@VOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FHe outlined that he had met with
OL,8,Ffemale officers and one of a number of
OL,9,Finitiatives to spur on cultural change
OL,10,Fwas having officers "commit to a
OL,11,Fstatement of intent with regards to
OL,12,Four values and our behaviours".
OL,14,FHe said: "I can absolutely assure you
OL,15,Fthat this type of behaviour, it makes
OL,16,Fme so angry, the members of this
OL,17,Fsenior team so angry, because I know,
OL,18,Fbecause of the work that the rank and
OL,19,Ffile do, some of which I described in
OL,20,Fmy opening remarks, this undermines
OL,21,Feverything we're trying to achieve.
OL,26,@rD@UOUtD@^O]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"It goes to recruitment, it goes to
OL,8,Ftrust in cops, goes to reporting, so
OL,9,Fwe will work incredibly closely with
OL,10,Fthe ombudsman to make sure that, and
OL,11,Fthere will be, I think, almost
OL,12,Fcertainly, quite considerably
OL,13,Fhistorical cases that will emerge from
OL,14,Fthis work.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1772733966
OL,3,CPSNI chief to 'relentlessly pursue'
OL,4,Cofficers abusing position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"And I would encourage anyone with any
OL,8,Fnegative experience or any information
OL,9,Fabout any such wrongdoing to please
OL,10,Fcome forward and report it to either
OL,11,Fourselves or the ombudsman so that we
OL,12,Fcan clear house with regards to these
OL,13,Fbehaviours."
OL,15,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,16,FITVX
